But as soon as Daniel knew that the decree had been signed, he went to his house,

00:07:10.259 --> 00:07:16.180
which had the windows of his roof chamber open towards Jerusalem.

00:07:17.620 --> 00:07:26.259
And three times a day, he got down on his knees and prayed and offered

00:07:26.259 --> 00:07:33.139
praise before his God, as he had regularly done prior to this.

00:07:34.740 --> 00:07:44.899
At that time, those men burst in and found Daniel petitioning and pleading for a favor before

00:07:44.899 --> 00:07:54.180
his God. My wife, Gloria, and I used to get down on our knees to pray before going to bed.

00:07:54.660 --> 00:07:59.220
Now that we're old, we just sit on the side of the bed and pray.

00:07:59.220 --> 00:08:02.019
If we get down, we can't get up.

00:08:02.019 --> 00:08:08.060
Keep in mind that prayer will produce in you joy.

00:08:08.060 --> 00:08:11.250
You're not alone.

00:08:11.250 --> 00:08:13.810
Jehovah is with you.

00:08:13.810 --> 00:08:17.569
